headline: PJM’s market monitor urges FERC to review Amazon data center’s effect on costs, reliability
summary: The issue centers on an unprecedented agreement between PECO Energy and Amazon Data Services that aims to protect utility customers from costs related to a planned data center complex in Pennsylvania.
